question: Which characters have a book1BetweennessCentrality greater than 2000?
cypher:
MATCH (c:Character)
WHERE c.book1BetweennessCentrality > 2000
RETURN c.name AS character, c.book1BetweennessCentrality AS centrality
typeql: match $c isa character, has name $n, has centrality $cent; sort $cent desc; limit 5; fetch { "name": $n, "centrality": $cent };

question: List the top 3 characters with the highest book45PageRank.
cypher:
MATCH (c:Character)
RETURN c.name, c.book45PageRank
ORDER BY c.book45PageRank DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $c isa character, has name $n, has pagerank $pr; sort $pr desc; limit 5; fetch { "name": $n, "pagerank": $pr };

question: Find all characters involved in an INTERACTS relationship with a weight below 10, limit to 5 results.
cypher:
MATCH (c1:Character)-[i:INTERACTS]->(c2:Character)
WHERE i.weight < 10
RETURN c1.name, i.weight, c2.name
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $c1 isa character, has name $n1; $c2 isa character, has name $n2; (character1: $c1, character2: $c2) isa interacts, has weight $w; limit 5; fetch { "char1": $n1, "char2": $n2, "weight": $w };
